title: Test Gig Request After Payment
notes: We’re developing a smart gated community in Lagos and need a freelancer to design an economic model that supports a self-sustaining ecosystem. The right partner will help us structure a blueprint that blends financial viability with innovation in sustainable living.

title: Pricing & ticket page design for the NATIVELAND music festival
notes: We’re producing the next NATIVELAND music festival and need a freelancer to design a sleek, conversion-focused pricing and ticketing page. The page should capture NATIVELAND’s bold creative identity while making it seamless for fans to explore ticket tiers, add-ons, and secure their purchase. The ideal partner will deliver a design that is visually iconic, mobile-first, and optimized for high sales.

milestones.title: Phase One: Research & Wireframing
milestones.description: Study NATIVELAND’s brand style, audience expectations, and competitor ticketing flows. Deliver wireframes and user journeys that prioritize clarity and excitement.

title: Event Marketing & Page Design for ROBLOX World Builders Championship – West Africa Regional Finals (Lagos)
notes: We’re hosting the ROBLOX World Builders Championship – West Africa Regional Finals in Lagos, and we need a freelancer to design a high-impact marketing and event page. The page should capture the energy of competitive gaming while making it simple for fans, teams, and sponsors to get information, register, and engage. The ideal partner will deliver a design that is bold, interactive, and aligned with both ROBLOX’s creative culture and esports best practices.

milestones.title: Phase 1 – Research & Concept Wireframing
milestones.description: Analyze top esports event pages and ROBLOX brand guidelines, then deliver wireframes for registration, ticketing, and event info flows tailored for a West African audience.
